grade_book

Class GradeBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • grade_book.GradeBook

  • public class GradeBook
extends java.lang.Object

    Uses an input text file (inFile) to instantiate student information, then calculates their average grade and letter grade, finally writes the formatted data to a new text file.

    Since:
    1.0 (04/07/2017)
    Version:
    1.0.1 (01/13/2019)
    Author:
    Brady Lange - LinkedIn
